                  {
                     "text": "<p class=\"desc\"><img id=\"imgAtlatl\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgAtlatl', '0%')\" src=\"\" class=\"imgcenter\"/><b>Figura 7</b>: Perfil de ornamento de un guerrero. © The Metropolitan Museum of Art, New York (<htcite0> ).</p>",
                     "source": [
